<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Why do you thing he needs one? :) He is married to his job. And he already has a family. His daughter. Of course, she is an adult now but that is what<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Why do you thing he needs one? :) He is married to his job. And he already has a family. His daughter. Of course, she is an adult now but that is what we get when we are getting old, spouse or no spouse.<br /><br />But seriously, he does not need a partner.. even if it seems to him that he needs one.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
